<ProseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Who we are, why we test AI tools the way we do, and how we make money."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'About', href: '/about' }]}
>
  <h1>About AI Tools Review</h1>
  <p>
    AI Tools Review is an independent publication that exists for one reason: there are far more AI products being launched than any reasonable buyer can keep up with, and almost none of the marketing tells you whether the thing is actually good.
  </p>
  <p>
    We pay for accounts. We use the tools on real work. We write down what broke, what surprised us, what we'd actually recommend to a friend — and we update those reviews when the products change.
  </p>

  <h2>What we cover</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Writing assistants and copy tools</li>
    <li>Image and video generators</li>
    <li>Code assistants and dev tooling</li>
    <li>Research, summarization, and knowledge tools</li>
    <li>Voice, transcription, and meeting tools</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Who's behind it</h2>
  <p>This site is edited by a single human reviewer with a background in software and content. See our <a href="/methodology">methodology</a> for how reviews are produced, and our <a href="/disclosure">disclosure</a> for affiliate relationships.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Get in touch on the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
</ProseLayout>
